text: Qin Haiyang (born 17 May 1999) is a Chinese swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in swimming Category:Asian Games gold medalists for China Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for China Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
